\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces The Edit Clustering Score (ECS) pipeline. Given a text pair, a word-level LCS diff extracts edit positions; the Index of Dispersion of inter-edit gaps quantifies spatial clustering. Near-duplicates (contiguous splice) produce one large block and low IoD; thematic near-matches produce many small scattered edits and high IoD. The inverted score (1/IoD or equivalently $-$IoD) serves as the near-duplicate signal.}}{3}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:fig1}{{1}{3}{The Edit Clustering Score (ECS) pipeline. Given a text pair, a word-level LCS diff extracts edit positions; the Index of Dispersion of inter-edit gaps quantifies spatial clustering. Near-duplicates (contiguous splice) produce one large block and low IoD; thematic near-matches produce many small scattered edits and high IoD. The inverted score (1/IoD or equivalently $-$IoD) serves as the near-duplicate signal}{figure.1}{}}
